Ceph-Rados version 0.04
=======================

This module provides a very limited subset of the librados API,
currently just read/write/stat and lists.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires that you have the librados installed, available
as either librados-dev under Ubuntu or from:

  http://ceph.com/resources/downloads/

